Summary:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The sub-prime mortgage bubble arose from broad acceptance that phenomena
 would work that had never before been seen in action.
 The analysis of investment vehicles should entail a) the application of
 skepticism and conservative assumptions and b) examination over a long
 history that includes some trying times.
 These things were clearly missing.
\end_layout

